TARGET.DESCRIPTION: This source is a flat file which contains the biographic data of the student provided by precode
TARGET.NAME: STUDENT_BIO_DATA_FLAT

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This map will split preid file into three files (BIO, DEMO, HIER ) and assigns precode_id to each student.
MAPPING.NAME: m_Preid_File_Split

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
DECODE(TRUE,
LENGTH(Teacher_Last_Name_v)>12, IIF (Teacher_Last_Name_v='UNKNOWN' AND Teacher_First_Name_v='UNKNOWN','UNKNOWN', SUBSTR(Teacher_Last_Name_v,1,12) || ' ' || SUBSTR(Teacher_First_Name_v,1,2)),
LENGTH(Teacher_Last_Name_v)=12, IIF (Teacher_Last_Name_v='UNKNOWN' AND Teacher_First_Name_v='UNKNOWN','UNKNOWN', Teacher_Last_Name_v || ' ' || SUBSTR(Teacher_First_Name_v,1,2)),
LENGTH(Teacher_Last_Name_v)<12, IIF (Teacher_Last_Name_v='UNKNOWN' AND Teacher_First_Name_v='UNKNOWN','UNKNOWN', Teacher_Last_Name_v || ' ' || SUBSTR(Teacher_First_Name_v,1,(14-LENGTH(Teacher_Last_Name_v)))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Teacher_Code_out

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
'M'
--Assingned constant "M' for georgia pilot since all students will take either MATH/READING and there is no value to determine the subject.
--For futher enhancement we can assign the value which can detremine the subjects/ subjects a student is going to retake.
--The values should be
--M- Math --R- Reading --B-Both
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Subject_out
